PlasmaGraph JavaDocs Page

Packages 
Package Description
HelpManual
Help File classes.
org.pvg.plasmagraph
Contains the main method that initiates the program.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.controllers
Contains intermediary classes between the view and model classes.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.models
Contains the processing classes of their respective Views or Controllers.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.tests
Package containing all the program's testing methods.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils
Data- and Exception-related tools.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.data
Data containers such as DataSet and HeaderData.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.data.readers
Various file readers for different data files.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.exceptions
Collection of all named Exceptions the program can throw.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.graphs
Core graphing classes, such as XYGraph.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.template
Settings-related tools.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.tools
Interpolation- and Outlier-related tools to measure correctness.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.tools.interpolation
Interpolation-creating classes.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.tools.outlierscan
Outlier Scanning classes.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.tools.outlierscan.distances
Used in the parent package to contain the variety of methods to calculate maximum acceptable distance between points.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.tools.outlierscan.methods
Used in the parent package to contain the variety of methods to find outliers.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.types
Helper classes detailing option types within certain categories.
org.pvg.plasmagraph.views
Contains GUI classes for the program.
